column5: I guess your gettn' ready for work, I am going fishing.
as is me!   'cept I am not using an auger  - mmmm cofffeee

Thanks Tom, rub it in why don't ya?  sheesh...lol  have a great day, looking forward to reading your report when I get home tonight.  Fishdawg, have a blast...along with anyone else heading out today.  Maureen
For sure I will report, if I am not too tired. Take care now.
Have a good day Tom & don't forget the camera
Good Morning!, and Good Luck to all going fishin' today! Be careful and take lotsa pics.  I'll be slaving out in the yard on the fence today...
